@model IEnumerable<PMTs.DataAccess.ComplexModel.ChangeBoardNewMaterial>
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IViewLocalizer Localizer

<table id="ChangeFactoryNewMaterialTable" class="table table-bordered color-table">
    <thead>
        <tr class="color-table text-center">
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["Create Status"]</th>
            <th style="width:120px">@Localizer["PDIS Status"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["Factoryเดิม"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["Matเดิม"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["New_Material No"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["Price"]</th>
            <th style="width:90px"> @Localizer["PC"]</th>
            <th style="width:200px">@Localizer["Customer Name"]</th>
            <th style="width:150px">@Localizer["Description"]</th>
            <th style="width:150px">@Localizer["Hierarchy"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["Cost"]</th>
            <th style="width:150px">@Localizer["Board"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["BoxType"]</th>
            <th style="width:100px">@Localizer["Machine"]</th>
            <th style="width:500px">@Localizer["Error Message"]</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        @foreach (var item in Model)
        {
            <tr>
                @if (item.IsCreatedSuccess)
                {
                    <td class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-check-circle" aria-hidden="true" style="color: green;"></i></td>
                }
                else
                {
                    <td class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-times-circle" aria-hidden="true" style="color: red;"></i></td>
                }

                <td class="text-center">@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.PdisStatus)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.CopyFactoryCode)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.CopyMaterialNo)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.MaterialNo)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Price)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.PC)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.CustName)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Description)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Hierarchy)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Cost)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Board)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.BoxType)</td>
                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Machine)</td>

                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(item.ErrorMessage) && !item.IsCreatedSuccess)
                {
                    <td class="text-danger" style="font-weight:400">
                        @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.ErrorMessage)
                    </td>
                }
                else
                {
                    <td></td>
                }
            </tr>
        }
    </tbody>
</table>